{"tid":668742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[There做野]小草單案好邪 主審法官病左要長期治療","createTime":"2018-05-18T01:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T16:55:15.000Z","uid":87973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4a4d2eb564278111bc0ab8e7d0585185c9c8ec41","tid":668742,"uid":87973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:27:51.000Z","msg":"之前已經有單鑑證科阿sir因為單案變左偷拍犯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家到主審法官病重 到底背後係唔係有乜野影響緊單案進展 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n石棺藏屍案法官因病須治療　法庭解散陪審團<br />\n2018-05-17 HKT 11:39<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1396832_1_L_20180517115524.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1396832_1_L_20180517115524.jpg&h=905a8bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣石棺藏屍案早上在高等法院續審，主審法官李瀚良因身體不適而缺席，他需要立即接受一段長時間的治療，法庭下令解散陪審團。<br />\n<br />\n代替李瀚良出庭的法官彭寶琴向7人陪審團表示，主審法官李瀚良有一段長時間未能上班，決定解散陪審團。她提醒陪審團，在解散後不可以與任何人討論案情，亦不可以在社交媒體講述案件，要求陪審團要遵守。<br />\n<br />\n彭寶琴又感謝陪審團過去7個多星期的努力，指這段時間一定對他們生活帶來影響，但當陪審員是盡公眾責任，形容各個人一直都好專心和盡責。<br />\n<br />\n案中涉及3名被告曾祥欣、劉錫豪及張善恒，同被控於2016年3月4日在荃灣灰窰角街一個單位內謀殺28歲男子張萬里。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1396832-20180517.htm?archive_date=2018-05-17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1396832-20180517.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2018-05-17&d=0lMTb%2Be1X1udiJY8OEQYvI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=25c789ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1396832-20180517.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2018-05-17&h=cdea412f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1396832-20180517.htm?archive_date=2018-05-17</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>查石棺藏屍案受壓　警影裙底判社服</strong><br />\n<br />\n港聞 ￼ ￼ ￼ ￼ ￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】鑑證科探員調查荃灣石棺藏屍案搜證，之後開始疑神疑鬼，又夢見死屍，壓力大增致患適應性障礙。為紓緩壓力，他在港鐵站內連環偷拍共14名女子裙底，早前在觀塘法院認罪，辯方昨稱他感到羞愧及後悔，將會被革職，最終他被判社會服務令200小時，另須繳付5,000元堂費。<br />\n<br />\n34歲被告柯榮發早前承認14項有違公德行為罪。辯方昨求情稱被告加入警隊8年，工作勤力，與同袍相處融洽，獲上司嘉許14次。調任鑑證科後有份調查石棺藏屍案，但工作壓力令他患適應性障礙症，影響他的情緒及自我控制能力而犯案。</em>"},{"pid":"18dd2ce2cd27d6f53433c1fed17fd12694b1d420","tid":668742,"uid":162268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:32:30.000Z","msg":"邪教獻祭嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1240fd014c37d19c2a1df120ef232fdbd8e958","tid":668742,"uid":41076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:36:01.000Z","msg":"Judgment Knight of <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a859d951867b405eae141d21c0e86aebfbd279b1","tid":668742,"uid":29880,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"聽3個痴線佬鳩up聽到噴血"},{"pid":"199497ece2fc6d2bbb9f5f5dfe7631d99b6790ad","tid":668742,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a859d951867b405eae141d21c0e86aebfbd279b1","tid":668742,"uid":29880,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:37:14.000Z","msg":"聽3個痴線佬鳩up聽到噴血"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:38:19.000Z","msg":"我都覺得係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac8b1450dc845bf6172eef1621ce099852523b1","tid":668742,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dd6c3d22b17ef66b5beeb11d190b9ef38d7c5c","tid":668742,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2f704331a9ad084bec56857839f4a023dfe709","tid":668742,"uid":133529,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"我入黎係想睇小草Ｄ　Ｊ圖，你俾個男人我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68eb16086516580dc5445f930e73ad2bba8b1e35","tid":668742,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:02:20.000Z","msg":"there 發功 非同小可 陪審團真係醒醒定定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9deec07911feb73b02f80d5e5052ea633b8d1364","tid":668742,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T02:03:15.000Z","msg":"真係有陰謀的話,下次可能係金鐘站玩返麻原彰晃最在行嗰樣嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係想睇而家變左霞關同大手町兩個站的混合體,出起事上黎點仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2017deae1c8e8163828c31b7b238405e5bb0c3d7","tid":668742,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"有無小草J 圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}